            <title>[MAHOUT-47] Point class is now redundant and should be removed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-47</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Point class that was introduced for clustering when Float[] was used instead of Vectors is no longer necessary and should be removed. The formatting for Vectors can now replace Point and the other methods should be moved so that the class and its test can be eliminated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
